          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22584824/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22584824/" class="">第198页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/rachine2/" class=" " title="rachine2">rachine2</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="22584824">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">国家不是仅仅取代现有的社会安排，它必须为自身提供一个可行的替代方案。

</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-11-19 21:28</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                国家不是仅仅取代现有的社会安排，它必须为自身提供一个可行的替代方案。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
